episodes.title: Opus: Dark Money, a Secretive Cult, and Its Mission to Remake Our World
episodes.description:
Full details here: https://transparencytaskforce.org/opus-dark-money-a-secretive-cult-and-its-mission-to-remake-our-world/

Our events are completely free to attend, and we’re committed to keeping them that way. Unlike many organisations, we don’t receive funding from big corporations or institutions - we rely entirely on the generosity of individuals like you.

If you’ve found value in what we do and would like to support us, please consider making a donation. Every contribution, no matter the size, helps us continue offering these events to the community.

Click here to make a donation: https://transparencytaskforce.org/donations/
